70
00:11:39,431 --> 00:11:40,801
Trời ạ.

71
00:11:42,801 --> 00:11:44,172
Tôi lẩm cẩm quá rồi.

72
00:11:47,172 --> 00:11:48,404
Con yêu, mẹ xin lỗi.

73
00:11:48,405 --> 00:11:49,308
